# Never Disable Checks

Never disable any quality gates. This includes:

- Type checks (`// @ts-ignore`, `// @ts-expect-error`, `// @ts-nocheck`)
- Linting (`// eslint-disable`, `/* eslint-disable */`)
- Formatting (prettier-ignore)
- Tests (skipping, commenting out)
- Git hooks (`--no-verify`)

## The Only Response to a Failing Check

Fix the root cause. Never work around it.

If a check is failing, the check is doing its job. The code needs to change, not the check.
